Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.41,0:01:07.42,SC Opening 2 Eng,,0,0,0,,...the slumbering legend
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.29,0:01:09.25,SC Opening 2 Eng,,0,0,0,,Scorching below us...
