Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.91,0:01:48.96,SC Opening 2 Eng,,0,0,0,,And the one to end it all will be Star Platinum!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:55.26,SC Opening 2 Eng,,0,0,0,,Our tale has begun and our time runs short
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.26,0:02:01.80,SC Opening 2 Eng,,0,0,0,,To end it all the Crusaders must continue onwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.80,0:02:09.65,SC Opening 2 Eng,,0,0,0,,Let loose your fists on this blank last page!
